title: Noises in the Night
description: In this Dateline classic, a community in Knoxville, TN, is shaken when a popular high school student is found murdered in her bed. In an exclusive interview, two students who helped police solve the case speak to Andrea Canning. Originally aired on NBC on July 16, 2018.
author: nbcnews.podcasts@gmail.com (NBC News)
